.\" ktsuss(1) manual page
.Dd December 21, 2024
.Dt KTSUSS 1
.Os
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh NAME
.Nm ktsuss
.Nd run a command as another user
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl hmuv
.Ar command
.\" ==================================================================
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
stands for
.Dq keep the su simple, stupid ,
and as the name says, is a graphical version (front-end) of
.Xr su 1
or
.Xr sudo 8
written in C and GTK+ 2.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl m Ar message , Fl \-message Ar message
Change default message in
.Nm
window.
.It Fl u Ar user , Fl \-user Ar user
Runs the command as the given user.
.It Fl v , Fl \-version
Print version and exit.
.It Fl h , Fl \-help
Print help and exit.
.El
